sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as run_gomb_smoke.py
    participant Enum as cycle enumerator
    participant Model as Gömb (3 shells)
    participant Eval as test AUC

    Note over CLI: --unrestricted-cycles=False (strict, default)
    CLI->>Enum: enumerate(e_train, s_train)
    Enum-->>CLI: pi(c) features (train-only)
    CLI->>Model: train + predict
    Model->>Eval: scores on e_test
    Eval-->>CLI: AUROC_strict = 0.9526 (5-seed)

    Note over CLI: --unrestricted-cycles=True (transductive)
    CLI->>Enum: enumerate(e_all, s_all)
    Enum-->>CLI: pi(c) features (incl. test-edge signs)
    CLI->>Model: train + predict
    Model->>Eval: scores on e_test
    Eval-->>CLI: AUROC_unrestricted = ? (5-seed)

    Note over CLI: audit sanity: --shuffle-train-signs on both branches
    CLI->>Enum: enumerate(shuffled)
    Enum-->>Eval: AUROC_shuffled
    Note over Eval: strict shuffled = 0.54 (no leakage)
    Note over Eval: unrestricted shuffled > 0.54 (leakage open)
